      • fastslow2

        public static <T> void fastslow2(java.util.List<T> list,
                                 java.util.function.Predicate<T> match,
                                 org.mitre.tdp.boogie.fn.TriConsumer<T,T,java.util.List<T>> consumer)
        Fast/Slow iterator for list of elements. When both the fast and slow iterators have a match the the consumer is called on the pair along with the list of skipped elements between the fast and slow iterators. Note - This method requires that there be at least two elements which match the supplied predicate to avoid silently never calling the consumer.
